                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "title": "<span style=\"font-size:26px\">National laws and regulations may not always ensure gender equality in employment</span>",
                    "content": "<p>In several parts of the world, however, laws and regulations currently in force do not adequately protect women from discrimination in employment nor guarantee equal remuneration for women and men. As of 2020, in 33 out of 188 (18%) countries and territories with available data, laws neither \u201cprohibit discrimination in employment based on gender\u201d nor \u201cmandate equal remuneration for work of equal value\u201d,<span class=\"footnote-index\"><a data-storymaps=\"MJ-ACTION-1615163182423\" data-storymaps-type=\"navigate\">5</a></span> despite the fact that 26 of those countries and territories have ratified ILO Convention No. 100 and/or ILO Convention No. 111. Among these 33 countries and territories with discriminatory laws, Brunei Darussalam, the Marshall Islands, Myanmar, Palau and Tonga have ratified neither ILO Convention No. 100 nor ILO Convention No. 111.</p>\n\n<p>Even when protective legislation exists, this does not always mean that women and men enjoy <a class=\"narrative-ref\" href=\"https://worlds-women-2020-data-undesa.hub.arcgis.com/app/4b31b21a4ccb41558b6f140a2327d225#NW11\" target=\"_blank\">equal rights</a> to/at work. <a class=\"narrative-ref\" href=\"https://worlds-women-2020-data-undesa.hub.arcgis.com/app/247cc2188f2146beacad35ef94ccf7fa#NW8\" target=\"_blank\">Discriminatory attitudes</a> on the part of both women and men towards women\u2019s employment may also contribute to unfair treatment of women and impede gender equality in employment.</p>\n",
                    "contentActions": [
                        {
                            "id": "MJ-ACTION-1615163182423",
                            "type": "navigate",
                            "index": 6
                        }
                    ],
                    "creaDate": 1615163183564,
                    "pubDate": 1615163183564,
                    "status": "PUBLISHED",
